name: Snips and Snails Photography $100 Gift Certificate (2014 newborn session only)
description:
Gift certificate value is $100 and may be used for any purchase (including session fee) for a 2014 newborn full/mini session at Snips and Snails Photography, Greencastle, PA. Gift certificate will expire 31 December 2014.  Upon receipt of payment, gift certificate will be mailed to payment address.
Newborns 2 weeks and under please at time of session.
Questions - call 717.597.0952
